<http://www.semanticweb.org/pablo/ontologies/2026/3/PAC2_Ontology#hasAssociatedRisk> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
